1
00:00:00,070 --> 00:00:01,530
[Episode 12]

2
00:00:01,530 --> 00:00:02,450
Taji

3
00:00:03,850 --> 00:00:04,770
Yes, boss.

4
00:00:05,930 --> 00:00:07,590
I'm not looking for these two.

5
00:00:13,970 --> 00:00:16,030
Come here, you little troublemaker.

6
00:00:16,210 --> 00:00:18,670
Do you have some obsession
with the number 2?

7
00:00:19,690 --> 00:00:22,650
It's not just about scoring two points.

8
00:00:23,770 --> 00:00:27,390
And those two from the threesome.

9
00:00:27,970 --> 00:00:31,650
And those two just now...

10
00:00:33,250 --> 00:00:34,510
Want to do it together.

11
00:00:43,850 --> 00:00:47,490
Are you a stalker?
Following me from Pattaya to here?

12
00:00:50,850 --> 00:00:54,570
Not stalking.
Just want to clear things up.

13
00:00:56,010 --> 00:01:00,810
Clear things up?
Which things exactly?

14
00:01:02,770 --> 00:01:05,330
That...

15
00:01:05,330 --> 00:01:06,930
How you used me and dumped me.

16
00:01:08,850 --> 00:01:12,450
Hey, aren't you misunderstanding something?

17
00:01:13,289 --> 00:01:16,090
About...

18
00:01:18,610 --> 00:01:22,690
You put your little brother
inside me.

19
00:01:25,690 --> 00:01:28,570
I'm the one who was taken advantage of.

20
00:01:32,330 --> 00:01:33,470
I don't care.

21
00:01:34,450 --> 00:01:37,810
But it definitely wasn't
just a one-night stand.

22
00:01:38,530 --> 00:01:40,250
A one-night stand?

23
00:01:46,490 --> 00:01:48,090
It's been twice already.

24
00:01:50,670 --> 00:01:52,270
Could it be...

25
00:01:54,530 --> 00:01:56,130
You want a third time?

26
00:01:57,009 --> 00:01:58,390
Here?

27
00:02:00,010 --> 00:02:01,350
Now?

28
00:02:03,530 --> 00:02:04,660
At this very moment?

29
00:02:05,610 --> 00:02:08,930
Ouch! Pull me out, quick!

30
00:02:12,570 --> 00:02:15,250
Damn, what the hell is this?

31
00:02:20,770 --> 00:02:23,450
Hey, who's this?

32
00:02:28,210 --> 00:02:30,890
Oh, he threw you in here too?

33
00:02:31,250 --> 00:02:33,930
Yeah, sigh.

34
00:02:35,650 --> 00:02:38,910
How is it?
Now you understand how it feels to be thrown away.

35
00:02:39,530 --> 00:02:41,930
Ugh, thrown into a garbage bin too.

36
00:02:42,770 --> 00:02:44,850
Hey, what are you doing?

37
00:02:46,010 --> 00:02:49,290
It's already this hard.
Do I really need to explain?

38
00:02:58,850 --> 00:03:02,170
[To Be Continued]
